  <brief_title>Effect of Chlorhexidine Gel on Bacterial Count During Fixed Orthodontic Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Chlorhexidine Gel on Bacterial Count and Orthodontic Brackets During Fixed Orthodontic Treatment; In-vivo &amp; In-vitro Study</official_title>
